## 🧾 Story: EIS Consent Write API Integration

### Objective
Implement method to push consent to CCMS.

---

### External API
POST /eis/consent/write

---

### Request
{
  "touchPointId": "MIF",
  "purposeSetId": "MIF_PURPOSE",
  "dpData": {
    "dpMobile": "9999999999",
    "dpEmail": "abc@mail.com",
    "dpIP": "127.0.0.1"
  },
  "consents": [
    {
      "purposeCode": "KYC",
      "purposeVersion": 1,
      "consentAction": "capture"
    }
  ]
}

---

### Response
{
  "status": "SUCCESS",
  "consentId": "12345"
}

---

### Development Steps
1. Create method:
   String writeConsent(String payload)
2. Encrypt request
3. Call API
4. Decrypt response
5. Extract consentId

---

### Acceptance Criteria
- Consent pushed successfully
- Returns consentId
- Handles failure scenarios